Road of Iran (maoist group)</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p align="left" style="background: transparent no-repeat; font-family: &quot;Liberation Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; text-align: left;"><span><span style="color: #333333;"><span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span lang="en-US"><span><b><span style="background: transparent no-repeat;">Proletarian Party of Purba Bangla(PBSP/Bangladesh)</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p align="left" style="background: transparent no-repeat; font-family: &quot;Liberation Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; text-align: left;"><span><span style="color: #333333;"><span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span lang="en-US"><span><b><span style="background: transparent no-repeat;">&nbsp;Communist Party of Switzerland (Red Faction)&nbsp;</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p align="left" style="background: transparent no-repeat; font-family: &quot;Liberation Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; text-align: left;"><br /></p><p align="left" style="background: transparent no-repeat; font-family: &quot;Liberation Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; text-align: left;"><span><span style="color: #333333;"><span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span lang="en-US"><span><b><span style="background: transparent no-repeat;">&nbsp;</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br /></p><p align="left" style="background: transparent no-repeat; font-family: &quot;Liberation Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; text-align: left;"></p><div><br /></div><p></p><b>declarati